IRS990.Desc: WRPDD ADMINISTERS FEDERAL PROGRAMS SUCH AS WELFARE TO WORK AND CHILDCARE FOOD PROGRAMS. WRPDD ALSO ADMINISTERS ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT PROGRAMS SUCH AS REVOLVING LOANS AND INTERMEDIARY LOANS.

SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE DISTRICT HAS BEEN RECOGNIZED AS EXEMPT FROM INCOME TAXES UNDER SECTION 501 OF THE INTERNAL REVENUE CODE AND A SIMILAR PROVISION OF STATE LAW. HOWEVER, THE DISTRICT IS SUBJECT TO FEDERAL INCOME TAX ON ANY UNRELATED BUSINESS TAXABLE INCOME. MANAGEMENT ANNUALLY REVIEWS ITS TAX POSITION AND HAS DETERMINED THAT THERE ARE NO MATERIAL UNCERTAIN TAX POSITIONS THAT REQUIRE RECOGNITION IN THE FINANCIAL STATEMENTS. THE PAST THREE YEARS ARE STILL OPEN AND ARE SUBJECT TO IRS EXAMINATION.
